accd (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix chat BOP argument parsing, /clear, /cleartp, track name bounds check.
  * Fix session standings sort to use session type instead of phase.
  * Add upper bound check on car_id in lap and sector handlers.
  * Move tick phase-tracking state into SessionState for correct session resets.
  * Fix monitor protocol to use actual session, weather, and config data.
  * Fix results JSON writer to escape strings and check fclose.
  * Fix bans_remove NULL dereference and bans_save silent write failure.
  * Enforce CONN_DISCONNECT: kicked/banned clients are now actually dropped.
  * Add SO_SNDTIMEO on client sockets to prevent slow clients from stalling.
  * Fix CI version detection for Fedora and Ubuntu, remove duplicate builds.

 -- Renaud Allard <renaud@allard.it>  Wed, 09 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0200

